re.com/2019/12/box-office-portrait-of-a-lady-on-fire-the-amazon-aeronauts-1202195343/ |title=Neon's 'Portrait of a Lady on Fire' Grabs Arthouse Crowd, Amazon's 'The Aeronauts' Deflates |website=[[IndieWire]] |date=December 8, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208200822/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/box-office-portrait-of-a-lady-on-fire-the-amazon-aeronauts-1202195343/ |archivedate=December 8, 2019 |accessdate=December 8, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SeventhWeekend\">{{cite web |last=Brueggemann |first=Tom |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/box-office-oscar-contenders-uncut-gems-bombshell-malick-a-hidden-life-1202197382/ |title='Uncut Gems' and 'Bombshell' Soar, Malick's 'A Hidden Life' Drags |website=[[IndieWire]] |date=December 15, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215210213/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/box-office-oscar-contenders-uncut-gems-bombshell-malick-a-hidden-life-1202197382/ |archivedate=December 15, 2019 |accessdate=December 15, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EighthWeekend\">{{cite web |last=Brueggemann |first=Tom |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/holiday-box-office-specialized-movies-a-hidden-life-bombshell-parasite-1202198948/ |title=As Specialized Movies Face Holiday Box Office Storm, 'Parasite' Hangs Tight |website=[[IndieWire]] |date=December 22, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223165208/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/holiday-box-office-specialized-movies-a-hidden-life-bombshell-parasite-1202198948/ |archivedate=December 23, 2019 |accessdate=December 23, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NinthWeekend\">{{cite web |last=Brueggemann |first=Tom |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/1917-just-mercy-uncut-gems-box-office-1202199518/ |title='1917' Starts Strong, 'Just Mercy' Shows Promise, but 'Uncut Gems' Dominates Box Office |website=[[IndieWire]] |date=December 29, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230115911/https://www.indiew