ar Cinematography Survey: Here Are the Cameras and Lenses Used to Shoot 42 Awards Contenders |date=November 20, 2019 |website=[[IndieWire]] |accessdate=November 29, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121133739/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/11/cameras-lens-2020-oscar-contenders-best-cinematography-1202187839/ |archivedate=November 21, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NewYorkPost\">{{cite web |url=https://nypost.com/2017/11/19/the-real-story-of-the-man-who-murdered-jimmy-hoffa/ |title=The 'real' story of the man who murdered Jimmy Hoffa |website=[[New York Post]] |date=November 19, 2017 |author1=Kaplan, Michael |accessdate=November 19, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119184121/https://nypost.com/2017/11/19/the-real-story-of-the-man-who-murdered-jimmy-hoffa/ |archivedate=November 19, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Financing1\">{{cite web |last=Lang |first=Brent |title=Cannes: Martin Scorsese's 'The Irishman' Has Buyers Frustrated and Salivating (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://variety.com/2016/film/markets-festivals/cannes-martin-scorseses-the-irishman-has-buyers-frustrated-and-salivating-exclusive-1201773763/ |accessdate=May 22, 2016 |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=May 13, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516165559/http://variety.com/2016/film/markets-festivals/cannes-martin-scorseses-the-irishman-has-buyers-frustrated-and-salivating-exclusive-1201773763/ |archivedate=May 16, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Financing2\">{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |last2=Busch |first2=Anita |last3=Jaafar |first3=Ali |title=Martin Scorsese's Mob Film 'The Irishman' In Major Deal To STX After Heated Bidding War \u2014 Cannes |url=https://deadline.com/2016/05/martin-scorsese-the-irishman-stx-huge-deal-mob-films-cannes-1201756232/ |accessdate=May 22, 2016 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood|Deadline]] |date=May 15, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520143630/http://dea