ravis |title=The Irishman: Robert De Niro Recreated Iconic GoodFellas Scene To Test De-Ageing Tech \u2013 Exclusive |url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/irishman-martin-scorsese-robert-de-niro-goodfellas-test/ |website=[[Empire (film magazine)|Empire]] |date=September 1, 2019 |accessdate=September 1, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901144941/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/irishman-martin-scorsese-robert-de-niro-goodfellas-test/ |archivedate=September 1, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"HolyGrail\">{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2020/01/11/business/ap-eur-film-de-aging-holy-grail.html |title='Holy Grail' Digital Effects Rewinding the Clock for Actors |date=January 11, 2020 |accessdate=January 16, 2020 |website=[[The New York Times]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116200042/https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2020/01/11/business/ap-eur-film-de-aging-holy-grail.html|archive-date=January 16, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PacinoDeAging\">{{cite web |first=Jenna |last=Marotta |title='The Irishman': Al Pacino on Playing A 39-Year-Old Mobster |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/03/al-pacino-martin-scorsese-de-age-character-the-irishman-1201944128/ |website=[[IndieWire]] |date=March 27, 2018 |accessdate=September 5, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426150521/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/03/al-pacino-martin-scorsese-de-age-character-the-irishman-1201944128/ |archivedate=April 26, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Rapold\">{{cite web |first=Nicolas |last=Rapold |url=https://www.filmcomment.com/article/death-be-not-proud/ |title=Death Be Not Proud |website=[[Film Comment]] |date=November\u2013December 2019 |accessdate=December 2, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202182339/https://www.filmcomment.com/article/death-be-not-proud/ |archivedate=December 2, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Brody\">{{cite web |last=Brody |first=Richard 